{
  "stem": "7157.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because she knew that the Germans when they came like that, they always brought dogs with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sure enough, the Germans came up with the dogs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they sniffed and sniffed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the wood had such a strong smell that there was no way they could smell that there were a couple of little kids in this cupboard.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, we got out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The only other thing I remember in the ghetto was that I was always hungry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, there was never enough food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My mother being-- worked on the outside, and she would sneak food in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, they snuck food in-- put their food in the brassieres, put the food wherever you could think of, you couldn't possibly imagine-- and brought some food home every night.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Something, a piece of bread or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because there was just no food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the daily killings would go on and go on and go on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it was obvious that we had to do something drastic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So my mother tells the story, and I, of course, I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But she went to the rabbi-- there was a rabbi in Stanislawow, in the ghetto-- and said, what should she do, because she has her mother and does she-- and the rabbi's answer was, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you must save the children.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's your number one priority.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Save the children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if you escape, your mother becomes secondary, it's OK.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, she-- my mother just couldn't leave her mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the rabbi assured her that that was the proper thing to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, even-- I guess, even to this day, when there's a question in this house, here, today-- like, what should we do?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always tell my wife to go ask the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
